@693 = ~Sounds to me like that is your problem.~
@694 = ~I'd suggest you find some way to deal with it, because I am going nowhere.~
@695 = ~I thought it was clear what they were after. Ils me voulaient morte et c'est tout ce que tu as besoin de savoir pour le moment.~
@696 = ~Your demands means nothing to me. I have the tome and that's all I needed, just know that my quest is not over. J'aurai besoin de toi à nouveau un jour.~
